Package org.neo4j.internal.kernel.api

Interface KernelReadTracer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ReadTracer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OperatorProfileEvent, ProfilingTracer.ExecutionEvent, ProfilingTracer.TimeTrackingExecutionEvent
    public interface KernelReadTracer
extends ReadTracer
    Tracer of kernel API reads. The Kernel will callback the tracer methods on various key events of kernel reads, allowing a tracer to analyze the read patterns. Note: In the initial version of this tracer we only added the callbacks that were necessary to support cypher PROFILE dbHits, and some extra which makes testing easier. If we adopt this mechanism for other uses, it might be a good idea to add additional callback, extend some callbacks with more details, or differentiate callbacks (e.g. onNode) depending on the underlying read.
